eption)) {\n                return null;\n            }\n            throw exception;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static Object invokeGreeting(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] arguments) {\n        if (method.getDeclaringClass() == Object.class) {\n            return invokeObjectMethod(proxy, method, arguments);\n        }\n        if (\"greet\".equals(method.getName())) {\n            return \"Hello \" + arguments[0];\n        }\n        throw new IllegalStateException(\"Unexpected method: \" + method);\n    }\n\n    private static Object invokeObjectMethod(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] arguments) {\n        switch (method.getName()) {\n            case \"equals\":\n                return proxy == arguments[0];\n            case \"hashCode\":\n                return System.identityHashCode(proxy);\n            case \"toString\":\n                return \"GreetingService proxy \" + Arrays.toString(proxy.getClass().getInterfaces());\n            default:\n                throw new IllegalStateException(\"Unexpected Object method: \" + method);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static boolean hasUnsupportedFeatureErrorCause(Throwable throwable) {\n        Throwable cause = throwable;\n        while (cause != null) {\n            if (cause instanceof Error\n                    && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError((Error) cause)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            cause = cause.getCause();\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    public interface GreetingService {\n\n        String greet(String name);\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 22492, "output": 1703, "cacheRead": 11264, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35459, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780857671328, "responseId": "resp_0821a8188c74fc3e016a25bb48b52881938047232cbf140865"}}
